`IsBernoulliOn X u p P` means `HasLaw X Ber(u, p) P`.
`HasLaw X Ber(u, p) P` implies `AEMeasurable X P`.
`AEMeasurable X P` implies `AEMeasurable (Set.compl X) P`.
`Set.compl X = fun ω => u \ X ω`.

